--- !u!114 &11400000
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: a49675d3da19b054686ae9ecd58461ad, type: 3}
  m_Name: option1 Lumena First
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::DialogueData
  lines:
  - speakerName: Lumena
    text: You stand in Aurelia Woods. Long ago, this forest was a place of balance
      where energy flowed gently through every root, every stone, every living form.
    voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
    typingSpeed: 0.03
    showOptionsHere: 0
    jumpBackToPreviousDialogue: 0
    previousDialogueLineIndex: 0
    speakerSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 05ab1f653215476409a566237c2bb668, type: 3}
    isLeftSpeaker: 0
    leftPortrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: c0c12ae43e657414daba01b6fa3e183f, type: 3}
    customFont: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 84c1d05c69deacd4cb1362b81cba58e6, type: 2}
  - speakerName: Lumena
    text: "My people tended to these currents. We shaped them, guided them\u2026
      and in return, the planet shared its strength with us."
    voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
    typingSpeed: 0.03
    showOptionsHere: 0
    jumpBackToPreviousDialogue: 0
    previousDialogueLineIndex: 0
    speakerSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 9d1852908ff850847b5159c766e754fd, type: 3}
    isLeftSpeaker: 0
    leftPortrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: c0c12ae43e657414daba01b6fa3e183f, type: 3}
    customFont: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 84c1d05c69deacd4cb1362b81cba58e6, type: 2}
  - speakerName: Lumena
    text: But that harmony has faded. What you see now are only fragments of what
      once lived here.
    voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
    typingSpeed: 0.03
    showOptionsHere: 0
    jumpBackToPreviousDialogue: 0
    previousDialogueLineIndex: 0
    speakerSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 9d1852908ff850847b5159c766e754fd, type: 3}
    isLeftSpeaker: 0
    leftPortrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: c0c12ae43e657414daba01b6fa3e183f, type: 3}
    customFont: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 84c1d05c69deacd4cb1362b81cba58e6, type: 2}
  - speakerName: Kaelaris
    text: "Fragments\u2026 but still alive. The energy here isn\u2019t dormant, it\u2019s
      trying to reorganize itself. Like a system running on corrupted data."
    voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
    typingSpeed: 0.03
    showOptionsHere: 0
    jumpBackToPreviousDialogue: 0
    previousDialogueLineIndex: 0
    speakerSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 9d1852908ff850847b5159c766e754fd, type: 3}
    isLeftSpeaker: 1
    leftPortrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: d01bd1b437def094c9a6780dbdad5281, type: 3}
    customFont: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 84c1d05c69deacd4cb1362b81cba58e6, type: 2}
  - speakerName: Kaelaris
    text: Your people guided these flows. Something must have disrupted them. What
      broke the balance?
    voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
    typingSpeed: 0.03
    showOptionsHere: 0
    jumpBackToPreviousDialogue: 0
    previousDialogueLineIndex: 0
    speakerSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 9d1852908ff850847b5159c766e754fd, type: 3}
    isLeftSpeaker: 1
    leftPortrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: d01bd1b437def094c9a6780dbdad5281, type: 3}
    customFont: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 84c1d05c69deacd4cb1362b81cba58e6, type: 2}
  - speakerName: Lumena
    text: "Astraeon\u2019s pulse didn\u2019t fail all at once. It was a slow fracture\u2026
      a disturbance that spread through the world\u2019s resonance."
    voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
    typingSpeed: 0.03
    showOptionsHere: 0
    jumpBackToPreviousDialogue: 0
    previousDialogueLineIndex: 0
    speakerSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 05ab1f653215476409a566237c2bb668, type: 3}
    isLeftSpeaker: 0
    leftPortrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: c0c12ae43e657414daba01b6fa3e183f, type: 3}
    customFont: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 84c1d05c69deacd4cb1362b81cba58e6, type: 2}
  - speakerName: Lumena
    text: The creatures changed first. Their forms twisted, their minds clouded.
      The planet tried to adapt, but the disruption ran deeper than we could act.
    voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
    typingSpeed: 0.03
    showOptionsHere: 0
    jumpBackToPreviousDialogue: 0
    previousDialogueLineIndex: 0
    speakerSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 05ab1f653215476409a566237c2bb668, type: 3}
    isLeftSpeaker: 0
    leftPortrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: c0c12ae43e657414daba01b6fa3e183f, type: 3}
    customFont: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 84c1d05c69deacd4cb1362b81cba58e6, type: 2}
  - speakerName: Lumena
    text: "You feel these remnants because Astraeon remembers what it once was. And
      now\u2026 it responds to you."
    voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
    typingSpeed: 0.03
    showOptionsHere: 0
    jumpBackToPreviousDialogue: 0
    previousDialogueLineIndex: 5
    speakerSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 05ab1f653215476409a566237c2bb668, type: 3}
    isLeftSpeaker: 0
    leftPortrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: c0c12ae43e657414daba01b6fa3e183f, type: 3}
    customFont: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 84c1d05c69deacd4cb1362b81cba58e6, type: 2}
  - speakerName: Lumena
    text: back to options
    voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
    typingSpeed: 0.03
    showOptionsHere: 0
    jumpBackToPreviousDialogue: 1
    previousDialogueLineIndex: 5
    speakerSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 05ab1f653215476409a566237c2bb668, type: 3}
    isLeftSpeaker: 0
    leftPortrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: c0c12ae43e657414daba01b6fa3e183f, type: 3}
    customFont: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 84c1d05c69deacd4cb1362b81cba58e6, type: 2}
  options: []
  isFinalDialogue: 0
